# ImpactLink — Complete Project Walkthrough

## 1. Project Description

**ImpactLink** is a full-stack crowdfunding platform built on the **MERN stack** (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js). It allows users to create fundraising campaigns, browse and donate to causes they care about, and track funding progress in real time.

### Core Features
| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Campaign Creation** | Authenticated users can create campaigns with titles, descriptions, images, goals, and date ranges |
| **Campaign Discovery** | Public browsing with filtering (Trending, New, Highest Funded) |
| **Donations** | Integrated Razorpay payment gateway for secure donations |
| **User Dashboard** | Personal view of campaigns created and contributions made |
| **Admin Dashboard** | Data visualization (Recharts), campaign management (activate/deactivate/delete) |
| **User Profile** | Editable profile (name, bio, phone, avatar) with password change |
| **Settings** | Notification preferences, dark mode toggle, account deletion |
| **Password Reset** | Email-based reset flow via Nodemailer with hashed tokens |
| **Animated UI** | React Bits-inspired components (SplitText, CountUp, FadeIn) using GSAP |

