## 3. Backend — File-by-File Breakdown

### Models (Data Layer)

| File | Purpose | Key Fields |
|------|---------|------------|
| [User.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/models/User.js) | User accounts | `name`, `email`, `password`, `bio`, `phone`, `avatar`, `settings{emailNotifications, darkMode}`. Has `bcrypt` pre-save hook and [comparePassword()](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/models/User.js#28-32) method |
| [Admin.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/models/Admin.js) | Admin accounts | `username`, `password`. Separate from users — has its own bcrypt pre-save hook |
| [Campaign.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/models/Campaign.js) | Fundraising campaigns | `title`, `description`, `goalAmount`, `raisedAmount`, `creator` (ref→User), `image`, `startDate`, `endDate`, `status`, `backers[]`, timestamps |
| [Donation.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/models/Donation.js) | Donation records | `campaign` (ref→Campaign), `donor` (ref→User), `amount`, `paymentStatus` |
| [Token.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/models/Token.js) | Password reset tokens | `userId` (ref→User), `token` (hashed), `createdAt` with 1hr TTL index |
| [Contact.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/models/Contact.js) | Contact form submissions | `name`, `email`, `message` |
| [Payment.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/models/Payment.js) | Payment records | Razorpay order/payment data |

### Controllers (Business Logic)

| File | Endpoints | Key Logic |
|------|-----------|-----------|
| [authController.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/controllers/authController.js) | `POST /signup`, `POST /login` | Input validation, email normalization, JWT generation (7-day expiry). Signup relies on User model's pre-save hook for hashing |
| [passwordController.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/controllers/passwordController.js) | `POST /forgot-password`, `POST /reset-password/:userId/:token` | Crypto token generation, SHA-256 hashing before DB storage, generic responses to prevent email enumeration |
| [userController.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/controllers/userController.js) | `GET/PUT /profile`, `PUT /change-password`, `PUT /settings`, `DELETE /account` | Whitelist-based field updates, password verification for sensitive operations |
| [adminController.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/controllers/adminController.js) | `POST /createadmin`, `POST /login`, `GET /profile` | Admin-specific JWT (stores `adminId`), protected admin creation |
| [campaignController.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/controllers/campaignController.js) | `POST /`, `GET /`, `GET /:id` | Input validation, date ordering check, goal > 0 check, field trimming |
| [donationController.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/controllers/donationController.js) | `POST /`, `GET /` | Donation creation with campaign/donor validation |
| [paymentController.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/controllers/paymentController.js) | `POST /create-order` | Razorpay order creation (amount in paise) |
| [admindashController.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/controllers/admindashController.js) | `GET /campaigns`, `PUT /campaigns/:id/status`, `DELETE /campaigns/:id` | Admin campaign management |
| [contactController.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/controllers/contactController.js) | `POST /`, `GET /` | Contact form submission and retrieval |

### Middleware

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [auth.js](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/middleware/auth.js) | [verifyToken](file:///d:/crowdfunding/impactlink-backend/middleware/auth.js#3-20) — extracts JWT from `Authorization: Bearer <token>`, verifies with `JWT_SECRET`, attaches `req.user = {id}` |

